{"tid":2198073,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"向郭偉强提私人檢控　陳志全稱律政司考慮是否介入案件","createTime":"2020-09-11T05:37:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T05:43:43.000Z","uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a0a8353fb40dc331be7d0396ccff800a13a71103","tid":2198073,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T05:37:40.000Z","msg":"人民力量陳志全早前向工聯會郭偉强提出私人檢控，指稱在5月立法會內務委員會主席選舉期間，被郭偉强拉跌倒地上。陳志全表示，收到律政司要求法庭押後審理有關案件6星期，以便有更多時間考慮是否介入案件，他對此表示反對。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全文:<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1549066-20200911.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1549066-20200911.htm&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fmXOOIBxzLj9jwnYVq%2FT7KE%3D&h=826a359c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1549066-20200911.htm&h=78047b64\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1549066-20200911.htm</a>"},{"pid":"fe2089074cb9e15902393e7b6a9196ba25b97669","tid":2198073,"uid":37874,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T05:38:37.000Z","msg":"殺人放火金腰帶<br />\n根本成個律政司都要制裁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9978f1a42af33ad42737fb0ae7f9aa57e4277e2","tid":2198073,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T05:40:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"723b0df46e13272bb475f5bf1c5e75cb0d6e11e7","tid":2198073,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fe2089074cb9e15902393e7b6a9196ba25b97669","tid":2198073,"uid":37874,"li